---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
const subjects = ['Software Developement', 'Computer Science', 'Artificial Intelligence', 'Data Analytics, Life Sciences']
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Hi, Ich bin Marcel und studieren an der Technischen Hochschule Ingolstadt im 6. Semester Bio- und Medizininformatik
      <br />
       Der Schwerpunkt meines Studiums sind unter anderem
      <ul>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
          <li>JavaScript</li>
          <li>React</li>
          <li>Solidjs</li>
          <li>Astro</li>
          <li>svelte</li>
          <li>Nodejs</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      coding, I'm passionate about design and 3D modeling and traveling.
      An unusual hobby of mine is collecting vintage passports, they're
      interesting pieces of history to me.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      While I have some preferred tools, I always choose the best one for the
      job, even if it's not on my usual list. My goal is to find the right
      solution for each project.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
